data.description: Welcome to this charming 2-story home, perfect for creating lasting family memories. This warm and inviting residence has been thoughtfully updated, featuring a modern kitchen with granite countertops, adding both style and functionality. The heart of the home, the kitchen, is sure to be a gathering place for family and friends. With its two stories, this home offers ample space for everyone to find their own cozy corner. Schedule a viewing today.
